PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE BEVERLEY A. BROWNE, a Territorial Court Judge of the Northwest Territories, as Senior Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice, effective April 1, 1999, as well as Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut, Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Northwest Territories, and Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Yukon Territory, during her tenure of office as Senior Judge of the Nunavut Court of Justice.
